OL,3,CWarning Spice-laced vapes in schools
OL,4,Cis 'emerging threat' despite
OL,5,Cdisposable ban
OL,7,FA fresh warning has been issued about
OL,8,Fschoolchildren using reusable vapes
OL,9,Fwhich are spiked with the synthetic
OL,10,Fdrug Spice.
OL,12,FIt comes as the government announced a
OL,13,Fban on disposable vapes from next
OL,14,Fsummer, to protect people's health and
OL,15,Fthe environment.
OL,17,FBut experts are warning this ban does
OL,18,Fnot go far enough, saying it "will not
OL,19,Fstop young people vaping".
OL,26,@zD@^OU{D@YO]
