OL,3,CWarning Spice-laced vapes in schools
OL,4,Cis 'emerging threat' despite
OL,5,Cdisposable ban
OL,7,FProfessor Chris Pudney from Bath
OL,8,FUniversity has been testing vapes
OL,9,Fconfiscated from schoolchildren around
OL,10,Fthe UK.
OL,12,FHe previously exclusively revealed to
OL,13,FITV News that it is now a "struggle"
OL,14,Fto find a school in England where
OL,15,Fvapes containing Spice were not
OL,16,Fpresent.
OL,18,FThe professor is now calling for the
OL,19,Fbill to be amended to tackle the
OL,20,F"emerging threat" of drug-laced vapes
OL,21,Fin schools.
OL,26,@uD@[OUuD@dO]|D@AOU|D@QO]
