OL,3,CWarning Spice-laced vapes in schools
OL,4,Cis 'emerging threat' despite
OL,5,Cdisposable ban
OL,7,FHe added: "We have found the synthetic
OL,8,Fdrug Spice is present in three
OL,9,Fquarters of schools sampled across
OL,10,FEngland. Spice is a very high-risk
OL,11,Fdrug, found almost exclusively in
OL,12,Fprisons, where it is associated with
OL,13,Fnearly half of non-natural deaths.
OL,15,F"Our work shows that Spice-laced vapes
OL,16,Fare almost entirely found as liquids
OL,17,Fadded to a refillable device."
OL,26,@oD@KOUwD@AOUyD@^O]
