OL,4,Cis 'emerging threat' despite
OL,5,Cdisposable ban
OL,7,FAn ITV News investigation also found
OL,8,Fthat vapes are being confiscated from
OL,9,Fkids as young as five in UK schools,
OL,10,Fwith thousands of teachers warning
OL,11,Fthey are causing significant issues in
OL,12,Fthe classroom.
OL,14,FThe British Medical Association (BMA)
OL,15,Fhas put its support behind the ban on
OL,16,Fdisposable vapes, but says it does not
OL,17,Fgo far enough to protect young people.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
