OL,4,Cis 'emerging threat' despite
OL,5,Cdisposable ban
OL,7,FIn a joint statement, Professor David
OL,8,FStrain and Dr Heather Grimbaldeston
OL,9,Ffrom the BMA described the UK as being
OL,10,Fin the midst of a "youth vaping
OL,11,Fepidemic".
OL,13,F"Cheap disposable vapes are just one
OL,14,Fof the ways that these products are
OL,15,Ftargeted at young people and a ban is
OL,16,Flong overdue," they added.
OL,26,@rD@SOUsD@IO]uD@AOUxD@NO]
