OL,3,CWarning Spice-laced vapes in schools
OL,4,Cis 'emerging threat' despite
OL,5,Cdisposable ban
OL,7,FWera Hobhouse, the Liberal Democrat MP
OL,8,Ffor Bath, has been vocal on the issue
OL,9,Fin Parliament. She wants the
OL,10,Fgovernment to do more, saying: "The
OL,11,Fnumber of children taking up vaping is
OL,12,Fdeeply alarming and so I am in full
OL,13,Fsupport of these steps to ensure that
OL,14,Fyoung people are not able to or
OL,15,Fencouraged to buy vapes.
OL,17,F"While the move to ban disposable
OL,18,Fvapes is extremely welcome, we also
OL,19,Fneed to look at addressing the
OL,20,Ftroubling risks to children's health
OL,21,Fdue to refillable vapes.
OL,26,@rD@`OUyD@AOU
