OL,3,CWarning Spice-laced vapes in schools
OL,4,Cis 'emerging threat' despite
OL,5,Cdisposable ban
OL,7,F"It's clear more needs to be done to
OL,8,Ftackle the growing issue of young
OL,9,Fpeople smoking Spice through
OL,10,Frefillable vapes and protect them from
OL,11,Fa life of serious addiction and health
OL,12,Fcomplications."
OL,14,FLast year, up to five million single-
OL,15,Fuse vapes were estimated to be either
OL,16,Flittered or thrown away every week in
OL,17,Fthe UK ` almost four times as much as
OL,18,Fthe previous year.
