OL,4,Cis 'emerging threat' despite
OL,5,Cdisposable ban
OL,7,FCircular Economy Minister Mary Creagh
OL,8,Fdescribed single-use vapes as
OL,9,F"extremely wasteful" saying they
OL,10,F"blight our towns and cities".
OL,12,FShe added: "That is why we are banning
OL,13,Fsingle-use vapes as we end this
OL,14,Fnation's throwaway culture.
OL,16,F"This is the first step on the road to
OL,17,Fa circular economy, where we use
OL,18,Fresources for longer, reduce waste,
OL,19,Faccelerate the path to net zero and
OL,20,Fcreate thousands of jobs across the
OL,21,Fcountry."
