OL,3,CWarning Spice-laced vapes in schools
OL,4,Cis 'emerging threat' despite
OL,5,Cdisposable ban
OL,7,FAccording to the Department for
OL,8,FEnvironment, Food and Rural Affairs
OL,9,F(Defra), England's vape usage had
OL,10,Fgrown by more than 400% between 2012
OL,11,Fand 2023, with 9.1% of Brits now
OL,12,Fbuying and using the products.
OL,14,FHealth Minister Andrew Gwynne said:
OL,15,F"It's deeply worrying that a quarter
OL,16,Fof 11-15-year-olds used a vape last
OL,17,Fyear and we know disposables are the
OL,18,Fproduct of choice for the majority of
OL,19,Fkids vaping today.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
