OL,3,CWarning Spice-laced vapes in schools
OL,4,Cis 'emerging threat' despite
OL,5,Cdisposable ban
OL,7,F"Banning disposable vapes will not
OL,8,Fonly protect the environment but
OL,9,Fimportantly reduce the appeal of vapes
OL,10,Fto children and keep them out of the
OL,11,Fhands of vulnerable young people.
OL,13,F"The government will also introduce
OL,14,Fthe Tobacco and Vapes Bill ` the
OL,15,Fbiggest public health intervention in
OL,16,Fa generation ` which will protect
OL,17,Fyoung people from becoming hooked on
OL,18,Fnicotine and pave the way for a smoke-
OL,19,Ffree UK."
